lyrics:
[Verse]
For God so loved the world, He gave His only Son
To save us all, redemption had begun
Through faith in Him, eternal life we'd find
The greatest love story of all time

[Chorus]
John 3:16, a message loud and clear
God's love shining bright, casting out all fear
His Son's sacrifice, our sins He did erase
In John 3:16, His grace we embrace
